OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDisability Minister: 'We   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcan do better' on          
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Femployment                 
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The UK's new disability minister has   
OL,6, admitted the government "has scope to  
OL,7, do better" when it comes to getting    
OL,8, disabled people into work.             
OL,10,FTom Pursglove, Minister for Disabled   
OL,11,FPeople, Health and Work, made the      
OL,12,Fcomment while announcing a new         
OL,13,FDisability Action Plan.                
OL,15,FHe is the third MP to hold the position
OL,16,Fin as many months.                     
OL,18,FThe Office for National Statistics     
OL,19,Fstates that 53% of disabled people in  
OL,20,Fthe UK are in employment.              
